long diagonal. Black's task to complete development is not trivial. Our best
chance is to return the pawn and develop the queenside as quickly as possible 
D) D)    In my opinion this is the most dangerous line. White is developing
typical long compensation dominating  with his Catalan bishop over the long
diagonal.Black task is to complete development is not trivial.Our best chance
is to return  the pawn and develop the queenside as quick as possible} Bxd2+ 8.
